title: Wall Street Breakfast: The Week Ahead
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: A heavy earnings calendar this week, including anticipated reports from Starbucks (SBUX) and Caterpillar (CAT). All eyes are on oil, as OPEC+ is expected to announce key targets, and Russian President Putin meets with Turkey’s Erdogan. Could food technology companies be the answer to a looming global crisis?
